{"type":"message","id":"8ed41ba9","parentId":"f1babeed","timestamp":"2026-04-15T00:00:00.932Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前-MyQuant选股] 执行盘前 MyQuant 选股：\n1. 先检查今天是否交易日（2026年休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216-20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001-20261007），休市则输出\"休市\"结束\n2. 运行: cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1\n3. 等待完成（约2分钟，Tushare调用较多），检查 outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/ 下 top_y5.csv 是否存在且是新生成的（检查文件修改时间）\n4. 如果成功，输出\"preopen 完成，候选池 N 只\"；如果失败，输出错误信息\nCurrent time: Wednesday, April 15th, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-15 00:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776211200930}}
{"type":"message","id":"a03ec001","parentId":"8ed41ba9","timestamp":"2026-04-15T00:00:44.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\nThe user has triggered a cron job that is supposed to execute pre-market stock selection using MyQuant. Let me break down what this cron job should do:\n\n1. Check if today is a trading day (2026 holidays are listed)\n2. Run a MyQuant pre-market selection script\n3. Wait for completion and check if the output file exists and is newly generated\n4. Output success or failure information\n\nToday is April 15th, 2026. Let me check if this is a trading day by looking at the holiday list:\n- 20260101, 20260102 - New Year\n- 20260216-20260220 - Chinese New Year period\n- 20260223 - possibly a holiday\n- 20260406 - Qingming Festival\n- 20260501, 20260504, 20260505 - Labor Day period\n- 20260619 - Dragon Boat Festival\n- 20260925 - Mid-Autumn Festival\n- 2026010-20260107 - National Day period\n\nApril 15th, 2026 is not in the holiday list, so it should be a trading day.\n\nNow I need to:\n1. Run the MyQuant preopen command\n2. Check for the output file\n3. Report results\n\nLet me execute the command step by step.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n<thinking>\n用户触发了盘前MyQuant选股的cron任务。让我按照步骤执行：\n\n1. 首先检查今天是否交易日：2026-04-15 不在休市列表中，是交易日\n2. 运行MyQuant的盘前选股脚本\n3. 检查输出结果\n4. 汇报执行情况\n\n我需要执行shell命令来完成这个任务。\n</thinking>\n\n今天是2026年4月15日，检查休市日列表发现不在其中，是交易日。现在执行盘前选股任务。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_047e8c32605e495e92c60a8f","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1","yieldMs":120000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":38943,"output":484,"cacheRead":3528,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42955,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":17762